            <a href="/intel/research" class="nav-item active" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:8px;color:#60a5fa;background:rgba(59,130,246,0.1);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;"><i class="bi bi-cpu" style="width:20px;"></i> AI Assistant</a>
